Class Node

java.lang.Object
  org.obd.model.Node
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AnnotationNode, CompositionalDescription, NodeSet, Statement
public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable

Fundamental unit of representation: any entity can be represented using a Node

equivalent to an RDF resource. can represent instances, relations/slots and universals

Note that Statements can also be nodes, in that they can be the subject or target of other statements

Author:
cjm
